1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Boot sensors and inspect the damaged power panel.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:13,200
Approach with the five fingers pre-shaped around the plug.

3
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:20,400
Close all five fingers and balance fingertip contact.

4
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:28,800
Reject injected camera bias using frame-sensor feedback.

5
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:36,600
Align the key and perform compliant connector insertion.

6
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:43,200
Rotate the bayonet collar to its mechanical stop.

7
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:49,200
Apply a proof-load impulse and recover measured displacement.

8
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:55,200
Press the guarded verification channel after lock confirmation.

9
00:00:55,200 --> 00:01:00,000
Hold safe pose and export states, actions, contacts, and labels.
